          <div class="flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl border border-red-900/30">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-red-900/30 text-red-400">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">High Entry Barriers</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-gray-300">Most blockchains require token purchases to get started, excluding new users.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl border border-red-900/30">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-red-900/30 text-red-400">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Centralized Economies</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-gray-300">Traditional blockchain economic models often replicate centralized power systems.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl border border-red-900/30">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-red-900/30 text-red-400">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Low Real Participation</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-gray-300">Passive users gain benefits without contributing to network growth.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-64 h-64 bg-indigo-500/5 rounded-full filter blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/20 to-purple-900/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div class="mb-2 flex items-center text-indigo-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
