              <div class="ml-3">
                <p class="text-sm text-indigo-300">
                  <strong>Did you know?</strong> Guardians can earn $ACR and $SOLV tokens without initial investment, just by contributing resources and time to the network.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Section>

